strings.Value: "Our backpacks grow more empty by the day. We should replenish our supplies!"
"Guess we'll need to cut our rations soon!"
"Don't worry: even if we're out of rations, we can always hunt."
"Your false optimism makes me sick. Why must you pretend? Do you fear that no one will like you if you show your true face?"
"Seems to me you don't eat nothing anyway. I wonder how you keep going!"
"At least our backpacks are lighter now, ha, ha. But tomorrow someone will have to go hunting."
"I have idea: let's get rid of the one who eat the most! Huh? Good idea? Why you look at Nok-Nok like that?"
"This is no desert. It's surely easy to find food... For someone familiar with these lands, of course."
